WEBVTT

00:04.188 --> 00:06.146
Yes, I think it's a brilliant idea.

00:06.147 --> 00:08.193
From this moment on,
I am going to be the farm manager.

00:08.194 --> 00:11.133
Don't expect everyone
to welcome these changes.

00:11.134 --> 00:12.176
No good will come of this.

00:12.177 --> 00:14.216
I want your baby, Nathan Appleby.

00:14.217 --> 00:18.138
For you and Mr Appleby,
to help you get with child.

00:18.139 --> 00:19.157
Do you believe in ghosts?

00:19.158 --> 00:22.196
In all your years of dealing with the
dead and the dying and the bereaved,

00:22.197 --> 00:25.154
have you ever seen anything
that you could not explain?

00:25.155 --> 00:26.205
Never.

00:26.206 --> 00:30.146
GWEN: I used to hear a boy's laughter in
the house. Then one day, no more laughter.

00:30.147 --> 00:31.196
Gabriel... They've seen him.

00:31.197 --> 00:35.203
Are you seriously telling me
you all saw a ghost?

00:35.204 --> 00:39.154
When I was looking for Charlie,
I saw lights rushing towards me.

00:39.155 --> 00:41.110
CHARLOTTE: Charlie's missing.

00:41.111 --> 00:42.180
SHE WAILS

00:44.165 --> 00:47.203
There are no ghosts.
There's just you and me.

