# So drink, boys, drink

55:44.723 --> 55:47.693
# See that you do not spill

55:47.694 --> 55:49.731
# For if you do, you shall drink two

55:49.732 --> 55:52.696
# For this is our master's will...

55:52.697 --> 55:54.686
MUFFLED: # So drink, boys, drink

55:54.687 --> 55:56.715
# See that you do not spill

55:56.716 --> 55:59.678
# For if you do, you shall drink two

55:59.679 --> 56:00.764
# For this is our master's will... #

56:06.705 --> 56:10.704
You are transgressing
against God and nature.

56:12.720 --> 56:16.674
Don't you think I want it to stop? But
whichever way I turn, the dead are there.

56:16.675 --> 56:18.662
Why are you lying?

56:18.663 --> 56:20.664
BABY CRIES

56:23.694 --> 56:26.727
I have given you everything.
Everything I have.

